        .section.bg-blue.text-white(name='features')
            .container.text-center
                h1.mb-4 Why Pterodactyl

                .flex.flex-wrap
                    .feature
                        span: i.icon.icon-lock
                        h3 Secure
                        | No MD5 here. We make use of the latest security standards such as BCrypt hashing and AES-256-CBC encryption.

                    .feature
                        span: i.icon.icon-browser
                        h3 Themable
                        | Every aspect of Pterodactyl is fully themeable using the Blade templating engine and your own CSS.

                    .feature
                        span: i.icon.icon-anchor
                        h3 Docker Based
                        | Pterodactyl is the first game panel to make use of Docker to control servers and harden your network.

                    .feature
                        span: i.icon.icon-wallet
                        h3 Free & Open Source
                        | Pterodactyl is 100% free and licensed under a MIT license. All of our code is completely open source as well.

                    .feature
                        span: i.icon.icon-beaker
                        h3 User Friendly
                        | Furious clicking and yelling is for video games. Pterodactyl's interface is so simple that even <a href="http://fallout.wikia.com/wiki/Dogmeat_(Fallout)">Dogmeat</a> could use it.

                    .feature
                        span: i.icon.icon-expand
                        h3 Scalable
                        | Whether you're a hosting company or some dudes playing video games, Pterodactyl has you covered.

